Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:19:00.05,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れの日も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:06.52,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君は今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:12.95,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}変わらず病気
